        "translations": {
          "en": "Ahmad b. Muhammad b. Yahya al-Attar (ra) narrated to us. He said: My father narrated to us from Ahmad b. Muhammad b. Isa from his father from Safwan b. Yahya from al-Is b. al-Qasim. He said: I said to al-Sadiq Ja'far b. Muhammad (as):",
